			<termAndDeftn vocab="Editor">Entity who assembles or refines a work for publication.</termAndDeftn>
			<termAndDeftn vocab="Interviewee">A person being asked questions by another person in a question and answer format.</termAndDeftn>
			<termAndDeftn vocab="Interviewer">A person who is asking questions of another person in a question and answer format.</termAndDeftn>
